    <item>
      <title>Open Settings</title>
      <link>/docs/configuration/open-settings/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/docs/configuration/open-settings/</guid>
      <description>&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Open Settings from the menu bar.&#xA;&lt;figure&gt;&#xA;      &lt;img&#xA;        src=&#34;/docs/configuration/open-settings/images/menu-icon@2x.png&#34;&#xA;        alt=&#34;menu-icon@2x.png&#34;&#xA;        style=&#34;width: 245px&#34;&#xA;      /&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;alert alert-primary&#34; role=&#34;alert&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 class=&#34;alert-heading&#34;&gt;Note&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;p&gt;If you&amp;rsquo;ve hidden the menu bar icon, open TrueWidget again from Launchpad while TrueWidget is already running to open Settings.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;figure&gt;&#xA;  &lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;/docs/configuration/open-settings/images/launchpad@2x.png&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;launchpad@2x.png&#34;&#xA;    style=&#34;width: 843px&#34;&#xA;  /&gt;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
